# OIBSIP Task 3 - Temperature Converter

Project Name: Temperature Converter

This project is a web-based temperature conversion tool developed as part of the Oasis Infobyte Internship Program. It enables users to convert temperature values between Celsius, Fahrenheit, and Kelvin through a simple and interactive interface.

Features:

* Convert Celsius to Fahrenheit and Kelvin
* Convert Fahrenheit to Celsius and Kelvin
* Convert Kelvin to Celsius and Fahrenheit
* Input validation for numeric values
* Clean and responsive user interface
* Beginner-friendly implementation

Technologies Used:

* HTML
* CSS
* JavaScript

